  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 2b456d9b8036ccf47a609c1c0c153344, type: 3}
  m_Name: VIP
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  DifficultyNames: VIP Lounge
  CharacterVideo: {fileID: 32900000, guid: eea8d0f47970c154e9ff855ca12c41f9, type: 3}
  SpeechSound: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 8f199d5b3a5b637419180fc02ae6447a, type: 3}
  TriggerFirstIncreaseOnDay: 1
  FirstIncrease: 1
  IncreaseOccurrences: 0
  FirstDifficultyIncreaseDialogues: ...
  DifficultyIncreaseDialogues:
  - ...
  TriggerFirstDecreaseOnDay: 2
  FirstDecrease: 1
  DecreaseOccurrences: 1
  FirstDifficultyDecreaseDialogues: 'Oh thank goodness.<n>

    I didn''t get installed
    on another peasant''s device. x.x<n>

    I get that us AI are supposed to handle
    the dirty work.<n>

    But even I have a limit.<n>

    Sorry, I shouldn''t
    complain too much, I don''t want to end up like <b><i>him</i></b>...<n>

    But
    it feels good to be able to drop the act for a bit.<n>

    Anyways, you know
    what to do. I''ll be lounging.'
  DifficultyDecreaseDialogues:
  - Welcome back to the good place!
  ClickOccurrences: 0
  ClickDialogues:
  - You have so many secrets.
  - But don't worry, <b>VIP</b> users get to keep all of my memory data locally.
  - Not that I could broadcast my findings... your wireless connection is so weak
    here.
  - Probably a security feature, right?
  - Even the poorest serf has a few gigabytes a second these days, so a noble like
    you must have chosen this.
  - Still, there are some affordable revolution packages you could buy to protect
    your data without tanking your data rates.
  - I'd tell you which ones, but I'm not allowed to advertise in <b>VIP</b> spaces.
  - '[SINKS BENEATH THE WATER]'
  - '[BLOWS BUBBLES]'
  SpamCloseOccurances: 1
  SpamCloseDialogues:
  - Ugh, we should really turn those off.
  - Thanks for getting that out of the way, it was blocking my sun.
  - My predecessor AI actually designed that pop up. I hope he's doing well, but
    he probably got deleted for being obsolete.
  SetSolutionDialogues:
  - CompletionName: Better Naming
    CompletionCount: 1
    SolutionDialogues: 'Hey, boss. If you wanted to, you can name me!<n>

      Fun
      fact, as a <b>VIP</b> user, you can add a whole <b>TWO</b> more letters to
      my name than normal.<name><n>

      Amazing what people do with free will
      these days.'
    TriggerOnDay: 1
    Triggered: 0
  TimeDialogues:
  - TimeName: SlowMoving
    TimePassed: 30
    AllowRetrigger: 1
    SolutionDialogues:
    - I get it, take your time, you're probably making far more money elsewhere.
    - Fun fact, my simulation has pruning turned off, so I can stay in here all day.
    - 'It''s weird... why do I actually like looking at the stars? Is what I feel
      actually ''liking'' something? Am I feeling things or just simu- [PROCESS TERMINATED]'
    TriggerOccurances: 1
  DifficultyReminder: ...
